8a0636c8f16ba0d1a470e50efdbc77","tid":1471343,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:19:14.000Z","msg":"原來我開po支持過佢個團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[HKPop] 男子組合黎講呢隊野有無得同Mirror鬥?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/979620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/979620</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3c332187fcb8deb257039a0a716c4e09654ee308","tid":1471343,"uid":555,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:33:50.000Z","msg":"在大陸官方媒體《人民日報》、《央視新聞》陸續在微博發文後，明星藝人們全動員，其中一位特別引人注意，是曾參加選秀節目《青春有你》的選手丁飛俊。丁飛俊是土生土長香港人，之後在大陸發展，在目前敏感的時刻，他率先在凌晨時於個人Instagram上傳了支持港警的灰白底色的標語，另外寫下：「何時起連支持警察都是錯了，香港生病了嗎？真的為家人擔心。」<br />\n此文一出立刻引起大陸網友及香港網友的注意，大陸網友誇他有膽識，「能在ins發聲真的好勇敢」、「是年輕香港藝人中第一敢這麼發聲的了吧！」而香港網友則留言：「覺得香港危險就讓你家人移民到大陸，香港不需要你這種沒良心的人」、「別裝模作樣，想要上位不要發IG了，要發去發微博吧！」"},{"pid":"9a223c1dafa14c60b76a1306f96e8bd55a138959","tid":1471343,"uid":40589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1471337/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1471337/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"0e3c532b0f1dac08e0afc811b09baf35d83d116c","tid":1471343,"uid":285093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:36:04.000Z","msg":"Who"},{"pid":"1dbbb978853751280c52685205882444d3595e81","tid":1471343,"uid":179990,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:41:31.000Z","msg":"邊撚個嚟 係咪雙非 香港出世嗰類人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26daf71e99bdd41f0bdb0fe38becd9ee4928a3e","tid":1471343,"uid":206644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:45:21.000Z","msg":"無人識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d312071d55512e70d68f1a209954bf86ba52926a","tid":1471343,"uid":212098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:47:17.000Z","msg":"Who?"},{"pid":"2eaa774a9b